-- Microcraft NextUI Device Manager --

local function aw(...) return write(...) end
local function p(...) return print(...) end
local function s(...) return sleep(...) end
local function tw(...) return term.write(...) end
local function scp(...) return term.setCursorPos(...) end
local function sbc(...) return term.setBackgroundColor(...) end
local function stc(...) return term.setTextColor(...) end
local function tc(...) return term.clear(...) end
local function tcl(...) return term.clearLine(...) end
local function r(...) return shell.run(...) end
local function sp(...) return textutils.slowPrint(...) end
local function sw(...) return textutils.slowWrite(...) end
local function fse(...) return fs.exists(...) end
local function pul(...) return paintutils.loadImage(...) end
local function pud(...) return paintutils.drawImage(...) end
local function pfb(...) return paintutils.drawFilledBox(...) end
local function su(...) return os.shutdown(...) end
local function re(...) return os.reboot(...) end
local function pdp(...) return paintutils.drawPixel(...) end
 
w, h = term.getSize()

function nilToBrak(str)
	if str == nil then str = "Brak" end
	return str
end

function mysz()
    local event, button, x, y = os.pullEvent("mouse_click")
    klik = {x, y, button}
    return klik
end

function findPeripherals()
	peripherals = {}
	
	peripherals[1] = nilToBrak(peripheral.getType("top"))
	peripherals[2] = nilToBrak(peripheral.getType("bottom"))
	peripherals[3] = nilToBrak(peripheral.getType("left"))
	peripherals[4] = nilToBrak(peripheral.getType("right"))
	peripherals[5] = nilToBrak(peripheral.getType("front"))
	peripherals[6] = nilToBrak(peripheral.getType("back"))

	return peripherals
end

function devMgr()
pfb(1,1,w,1,colors.blue)
stc(colors.white)
scp(1,1)
p("NextUI Device Manager")
pdp(w,1,colors.red)
stc(colors.white)
scp(w,1)
p("X")
pfb(1,2,w,h,colors.black)
scp(1,2)
stc(colors.white)
p("NextUI Compatible PC")
local char1 = "\149"
p(char1)
p(char1)
local char2 = "\131"
for i = 5,14 do
	scp(1,i)
	p(char1)
end

peripheralsFound = findPeripherals()

scp(2,5)
p(char2,"Top ", peripheralsFound[1])
scp(2,7)
p(char2, "Bottom", peripherals[2])
scp(2,9)
p(char2, "Left", peripherals[3])
scp(2,11)
p(char2, "Right", peripherals[4])
scp(2,13)
p(char2, "Front", peripherals[5])
scp(2,15)
p(char2, "Back", peripherals[6])

while true do
klik = mysz()

if klik[1] == w and klik[2] == 1 then break end
end

end

devMgr()

def move_zeros_to_end(input_str):
    integer_list = [int(x) for x in input_str.split(', ')]

    zeros = [x for x in integer_list if x == 0]
    non_zeros = [x for x in integer_list if x != 0]

    result = non_zeros + zeros

    return result

input_string = input()

output = move_zeros_to_end(input_string)
print(output)

-- This is a local script from my clan system
-- You can not count variables

local rs = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage")
local events = rs:WaitForChild("RemoteEvents")
local functions = rs:WaitForChild("RemoteFunctions")

--[ Events ]--
local joinEvent = events:WaitForChild("JoinClan")
local leaveEvent = events:WaitForChild("LeaveClan")
local editEvent = events:WaitForChild("EditClan")
local createClan = events:WaitForChild("CreateClan")
local deleteEvent = events:WaitForChild("DeleteClan")
local kickEvent = events:WaitForChild("KickPlayer")

--[ Functions ]--
local getClansData = functions:WaitForChild("GetClanDictionary")

--[ Player things ]--
local plr = game.Players.LocalPlayer
local plrClanValues = plr:WaitForChild("ClanValues")
local member = plrClanValues:WaitForChild("MemberOfClan")
local owner = plrClanValues:WaitForChild("OwnedClan")
local plrGui = plr:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")

--[ Frames ]--
local clanUI = plrGui:WaitForChild("ClanUI")
local clanCreateFrame = clanUI:WaitForChild("ClanCreateFrame")
local ownerClanFrame = clanUI:WaitForChild("OwnerClanFrame")
local memberClanFrame = clanUI:WaitForChild("MemberClanFrame")
local clansFrame = clanUI:WaitForChild("ClansFrame")
local messageFrame = clanUI:WaitForChild("MessageFrame")
local clansScrollingFrame = clansFrame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame")
local memberScrollingFrame = memberClanFrame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame")
local ownerScrollingFrame = ownerClanFrame:WaitForChild("ScrollingFrame")

--[ Buttons ]--
local openClansBtn = clanUI:WaitForChild("OpenClans")
local createClanBtn = clanCreateFrame:WaitForChild("CreateClan")
local deleteClanBtn = ownerClanFrame:WaitForChild("DeleteClan")
local saveChangesBtn = ownerClanFrame:WaitForChild("Save")
local leaveClanBtn = memberClanFrame:WaitForChild("Leave")
local createClanPromptBtn = clansFrame:WaitForChild("CreateClan")
local myClanBtn = clansFrame:WaitForChild("MyClan")

--[ TextBoxes ]--
local searchBar = clansFrame:WaitForChild("SearchBar")
local createClanName = clanCreateFrame:WaitForChild("ClanName")
local createIconId = clanCreateFrame:WaitForChild("IconId")
local createClanDescription = clanCreateFrame:WaitForChild("Description")
local replaceClanDescription = ownerClanFrame:WaitForChild("Description")
local replaceIconId = ownerClanFrame:WaitForChild("IconId")

--[ Layouts ]--
local clanLayout = clansFrame:WaitForChild("Layouts"):WaitForChild("ClanFrame")
local ownerLayout = ownerClanFrame:WaitForChild("Layouts"):WaitForChild("MemberFrame")
local memberLayout = memberClanFrame:WaitForChild("Layouts"):WaitForChild("MemberFrame")

local getData = {} -- Clans folder
local searchDebounce = false
local kickDebounce = false

function HideOtherFrames(otherFrame) -- Hide all frames (except otherFrame)
	for _, frame in pairs(clanUI:GetChildren()) do
		if frame:IsA("GuiObject") and frame ~= otherFrame and not frame:IsA("TextButton") then
			frame.Visible = false
		end
	end
end

function ThrowMessage(msg) -- Creates message frame
	task.spawn(function() -- New thread
		messageFrame.Message.Text = msg
		messageFrame.Visible = true
		task.wait(2)
		messageFrame.Visible = false
	end)
end

function CreateClanFrame(clanDict) -- Create clan frame
	if clansScrollingFrame:FindFirstChild(clanDict["Name"]) then return end -- If there is a frame.Name in the scrollingFrame then return
	
	local clone = clanLayout:Clone()
	clone.ClanName.Text = clanDict["Name"]
	clone.Description.Text = clanDict["Description"]
	clone.Icon.Image = clanDict["IconId"]
	clone.MembersCount.Text = (#clanDict["Members"] + 1).."/"..clanDict["Capacity"] -- +1 == members + owner
	clone.Visible = true
	clone.Name = clanDict["Name"]
	clone.Parent = clansScrollingFrame
end

function ClearClansScrollingFrame(lowerSearch)
	for _, frame in pairs(clansScrollingFrame:GetChildren()) do -- Iterate through clan frames
		if frame:IsA("Frame") then
			if lowerSearch then -- if search text ~= nil
				if string.find(string.lower(frame.ClanName.Text), lowerSearch) then -- Search logic
					continue
				else
					frame:Destroy()
				end
			end
		end
	end
end

function GenerateClanFrames(searchText) -- Insane Logic
	for _, frame in pairs(clansScrollingFrame:GetChildren()) do -- Clean clan frames
		if frame:IsA("Frame") then
			frame:Destroy()
		end
	end
	
	if getData ~= "Empty" then -- If clan's DataStore ~= "Empty"
		for clanName, clanDict in pairs(getData) do -- Get clans
			if #clansScrollingFrame:GetChildren() < 100 then -- No more than 100 clans in scrollingFrame
				if searchText ~= nil and searchText ~= "" then -- If search text ~= nil
					local lowerSearch = string.lower(searchText) -- To lowercase
					local lowerClanName = string.lower(clanName) -- To lowercase
					local searchResult = string.find(lowerClanName, lowerSearch) -- Clan text search
					
					if searchResult then -- If clan exist
						CreateClanFrame(clanDict) -- Create clan frame
					end

					ClearClansScrollingFrame(lowerSearch) -- See "ClearClansScrollingFrame" function
				else -- If search text == nil
					CreateClanFrame(clanDict) -- Create clan frame
				end
			else -- If #scrollingFrame:GetChildren() == 100
				break
			end

			task.wait(.1)
		end
	end
end

function CreateClickEvent(btn)
	local action = nil -- action == btn.Join or btn.Kick == button
	
	if btn:FindFirstChild("Join") then
		action = "Join"
	elseif btn:FindFirstChild("Kick") then
		action = "Kick"
	end
	
	btn:FindFirstChild(action).MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
		if action == "Join" then
			getData = getClansData:InvokeServer() -- Update clans data
			
			if (#getData[btn.Name]["Members"] + 1) < getData[btn.Name]["Capacity"] and member.Value == "" and owner.Value == "" and getData[btn.Name] then -- logic for max players limit
				joinEvent:FireServer(btn.Name) -- Update clan members (1 arg == Clan name)
				HideOtherFrames() -- Hide all frames
				ThrowMessage("Now you are a member of the: "..btn.Name) -- Message
			end
		elseif action == "Kick" then
			if kickDebounce then return end
			kickDebounce = true
			
			kickEvent:FireServer(tonumber(btn.Name)) -- Update clan members (1 arg == UserId)
		end
	end)
end

function CreatePlayerFrame(layout, userId, index, scrollingFrame, role)
	local cloneFrame = layout:Clone()
	cloneFrame.Name = userId
	cloneFrame.PlayerName.Text = game.Players:GetNameFromUserIdAsync(userId) -- Get player's name
	cloneFrame.Role.Text = role
	cloneFrame.Icon.Image = game.Players:GetUserThumbnailAsync(userId, Enum.ThumbnailType.HeadShot, Enum.ThumbnailSize.Size180x180) -- Player's avatar icon
	cloneFrame.ZIndex = index
	cloneFrame.Visible = true
	cloneFrame.Parent = scrollingFrame
	
	if scrollingFrame == ownerScrollingFrame and role == "Owner" then
		cloneFrame:FindFirstChild("Kick"):Destroy() -- The clan owner frame doesn't have a "Kick" button
	end
end

function LoadMembersList(clanName, clan) -- clanName == StringValue in player's folder
	local layout = nil -- Player frame layout
	local roleScrollingFrame = nil
	
	if clanName.Name == "MemberOfClan" then
		layout = memberLayout
		roleScrollingFrame = memberScrollingFrame
	else
		layout = ownerLayout
		roleScrollingFrame = ownerScrollingFrame
	end
	
	for _, frame in pairs(roleScrollingFrame:GetChildren()) do -- Clean members list
		if frame:IsA("Frame") then
			frame:Destroy()
		end
	end
	
	CreatePlayerFrame(layout, clan["Owner"], 1, roleScrollingFrame, "Owner") -- Owner player frame
	for i, userId in ipairs(clan["Members"]) do
		CreatePlayerFrame(layout, userId, i + 1, roleScrollingFrame, "Member") -- Member player frame
	end
end

function SetupPlayerClanFrame(frame, clanName)
	local clan = getData[clanName.Value] -- Get clan
	
	if clanName.Name == "MemberOfClan" then -- Logic for MemberClanFrame
		frame.ClanName.Text = clan["Name"]
	else -- Logic for OwnerClanFrame
		frame.IconId.Text = clan["IconId"]
	end
	frame.Description.Text = clan["Description"]
	frame.MembersCount.Text = (#clan["Members"] + 1).."/"..clan["Capacity"]
	frame.ClanIcon.Image = clan["IconId"]
	
	LoadMembersList(clanName, clan) -- Load clan members
end

for _, object in pairs(clanUI:GetDescendants()) do
	if object:IsA("TextButton") and object.Name == "Close" then
		object.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
			object:FindFirstAncestorWhichIsA("Frame").Visible = false
		end)
	end
end

function ApplyImagePreview(imageFrame, textBox) -- Set image to frame
	if textBox.Text == "" then
		imageFrame.Image = 0
	else
		local id = textBox.Text

		local success = pcall(function()
			id = "rbxassetid://"..tonumber(id)
		end)

		if success then
			imageFrame.Image = id
		end
	end
end

openClansBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	if not clansFrame.Visible then
		HideOtherFrames(clansFrame) -- Hide all frames except ClansFrame
		clansFrame.Visible = true
		searchBar.Text = "" -- Prevents bugs
		
		getData = getClansData:InvokeServer() -- Update ALL clans data

		GenerateClanFrames() -- Add clan frames to ScrollingFrame
	else
		clansFrame.Visible = false
	end
end)

myClanBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	local frameToSave = nil -- (OwnerClanFrame or MemberClanFrame)
	local roleInClan = nil
	
	if owner.Value ~= "" then -- If the player has his own clan
		frameToSave = ownerClanFrame -- OwnerClanFrame
		roleInClan = owner
	elseif member.Value ~= "" then -- If the player is in a clan
		frameToSave = memberClanFrame -- MemberClanFrame
		roleInClan = member
	else
		ThrowMessage("You don't have a clan!") -- "Message"
	end
	
	if frameToSave then
		HideOtherFrames(frameToSave) -- Hide all frames except FrameToSave (OwnerClanFrame or MemberClanFrame)
		frameToSave.Visible = true
		SetupPlayerClanFrame(frameToSave, roleInClan) -- Setup clan frame
	end
end)

leaveClanBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	if member.Value ~= "" then
		leaveEvent:FireServer() -- Updates clan members
	end
end)

createClanPromptBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	if member.Value == "" and owner.Value == "" then
		clanCreateFrame.Visible = true
		HideOtherFrames(clanCreateFrame) -- Hide all frames except ClanCreateFrame
	else
		ThrowMessage("You are already in the clan!") -- Message
	end
end)

createIconId.FocusLost:Connect(function()
	if clanCreateFrame.Visible then
		ApplyImagePreview(clanCreateFrame.ClanIconPreview, createIconId) -- Set image
	end
end)

replaceIconId.FocusLost:Connect(function()
	ApplyImagePreview(ownerClanFrame.ClanIcon, replaceIconId) -- Set image
end)

createClanBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	local name = createClanName.Text
	local desc = createClanDescription.Text
	local iconId = createIconId.Text
	
	if not getData[name] then -- If there is no clan with that name
		createClan:FireServer(name, desc, iconId) -- Creates clan
		HideOtherFrames() -- Hide all frames
		ThrowMessage("You have successfully created a clan!") -- Message
	end
end)

leaveEvent.OnClientEvent:Connect(function()
	HideOtherFrames() -- Hide all frames
	ThrowMessage("You have left the clan!") -- Message
end)

kickEvent.OnClientEvent:Connect(function(instruction)
	if instruction == "Kicked" then
		HideOtherFrames() -- Hide all frames
		ThrowMessage("You have been kicked from the clan!") -- Message
	else -- "Kick" instruction
		getData = getClansData:InvokeServer() -- Update ALL clans data
		
		LoadMembersList(owner, getData[owner.Value]) -- Update members list
		kickDebounce = false
	end
end)

deleteClanBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	if owner.Value ~= "" then
		deleteEvent:FireServer() -- Deleting clan from DataStore
		HideOtherFrames() -- Hide all frames
		ThrowMessage("You have successfully deleted the clan!") -- Message
	end
end)

saveChangesBtn.MouseButton1Up:Connect(function()
	if owner.Value ~= "" then
		local iconId = string.match(replaceIconId.Text, "%d+", 1) -- Only number
		local desc = replaceClanDescription.Text
		
		editEvent:FireServer(iconId, desc) -- Saving clan changes
		HideOtherFrames() -- Hide all frames
		ThrowMessage("Successfully changed!") -- Message
	end
end)

searchBar.FocusLost:Connect(function()
	if not searchDebounce then
		searchDebounce = true
		
		GenerateClanFrames(searchBar.Text) -- Add clan frames
		
		task.wait(.5)
		searchDebounce = false
	end
end)

clansScrollingFrame.ChildAdded:Connect(function(child) -- Clan frames for clans frame
	if child:IsA("Frame") then
		CreateClickEvent(child)
	end
end)

ownerScrollingFrame.ChildAdded:Connect(function(child) -- Player frames for owner clan frame
	if child:IsA("Frame") then
		if child.Name ~= tostring(getData[owner.Value]["Owner"]) then
			CreateClickEvent(child) -- Creates .MouseButton1Up event
		end
	end
end)

local function pdp(...) return paintutils.drawPixel(...) end

local w, h = term.getSize()
local maxListingsPerPage = math.floor((h - 3) / 2) 

local listings = {} 
local currentPage = 1


function loadListings()
    local listingPath = "/listings/"
    listings = {}

    if fs.exists(listingPath) then
        local fileList = fs.list(listingPath)
        for i = 1, #fileList do
            local filePath = fs.combine(listingPath, fileList[i])
            local listing = fs.open(filePath, "r")
            if listing then
                local auctionData = {
                    name = listing.readLine(),
                    quantity = listing.readLine(),
                    price = listing.readLine(),
                    nick = listing.readLine()
                }

                table.insert(listings, auctionData)
                
                listing.close()
            end
        end
    end
end

function drawUI()
	pfb(1,1,w,1,colors.blue)
	stc(colors.white)
	scp(1,1)
	p("Microcraft Market Alpha")
	pfb(1,2,w,h, colors.orange)
	stc(colors.white)
	scp(1,h)
	local char_box1 = "\142"
	local char_box2 = "\149"
	sbc(colors.blue)
	stc(colors.white)
	scp(w,1)
	p(char_box2)
	sbc(colors.orange)
	stc(colors.white)
	for i=2,(h-1) do
		scp(w,i)
		p(char_box2)
	end
	scp(w,h)
	write(char_box2)
end
	
	

function showListings(page)
	drawUI()
	stc(colors.white)
    local startIndex = (page - 1) * maxListingsPerPage + 1
    local endIndex = math.min(startIndex + maxListingsPerPage - 1, #listings)

    for i = startIndex, endIndex do
        local listing = listings[i]
        if listing then
			pfb(1, (i - startIndex) * 2 + 2, 3, (i - startIndex) * 2 + 2, colors.green)
			sbc(colors.orange)
			stc(colors.white)
            term.setCursorPos(5, (i - startIndex) * 2 + 2)
            print(listing.name, listing.quantity, listing.price, listing.nick)
        end
    end

    term.setCursorPos(1, h)
    term.write("Strona" .. page .. "/" .. math.ceil(#listings / maxListingsPerPage))
end

function main()
    loadListings()

    while true do
        showListings(currentPage)

        local eventType, key = os.pullEvent()
        if eventType == "key" then
            if key == 200 then
                currentPage = math.max(currentPage - 1, 1)
            elseif key == 208 then
                currentPage = math.min(currentPage + 1, math.ceil(#listings / maxListingsPerPage))
            elseif key == 28 then
                -- Enter
                break
            end
        end
    end
end

main()
